#  breadc distinctive features:
#    - CHAINED-BUILDER API similar in spirit to commander.js +
#      koa.js middleware patterns
#    - `breadc(name, opts)` factory + `.option()` for global
#      flags + `.command(name, desc)` for subcommands + `.action
